**The bridge between Mesh Analyzer + Pixel Analyzer = CAD skill.** The mesh analyzer already handles the 3D geometry side. The pixel analyzer handles the 2D compositing side. The CAD skill is the glue: it renders the 3D mesh into a 2D buffer using the perspective extracted from the background photo, then hands that buffer off to the pixel analyzer for integration.

